    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The state is stored in a special data structure called a Merkle-Patricia trie, inside leveldb. Imagine it as a prefix-trie containing all the accounts by address, where each \"leaf\" representing an account contains yet another prefix-trie containing all the stored state by hash. Spice this up with crypto guarantees instead of a plain prefix-trie, and you get the Merkle-Patricia trie. :)",
